## Information 

MessageWarden - an acceptation test for supercomputers

This program utilises RayPlatform.

## Features 

This is a program to test the network.

In particular, this tool will detect message corruption.


## Installation 

You need RayPlatform in the parent directory so that the symbolic link
resolves.

You also need mpicxx.

To compile:

	make


## How to run it 

	mpiexex -n 64 MessageWarden

